OL,6,FJennifer Webster, who's 25-weeks
OL,7,Fpregnant with her second child is
OL,8,Fbeing treated at the Cumberland
OL,9,FInfirmary, where she also gave birth
OL,10,Fto her first child.
OL,12,FShe said: "I was really impressed, it
OL,13,Fwas a little bit of a shaky
OL,14,Fafterbirth, I had a hemorrhage.
OL,16,F"Everyone at Carlisle was fantastic
OL,17,Fand really looked after me, and I felt
OL,18,Fcompletely in safe hands.
OL,20,F"I've had lots of midwife appointments
OL,21,Fout in the community.
