OL,3,CMaternity services praised by new
OL,4,Cmothers in north Cumbria
OL,6,FAmanda Kennett, associated director of
OL,7,Fmidwifery at North Cumbria Integrated
OL,8,FCare (NCIC), said: "We continue to
OL,9,Fimprove year on year and to see
OL,10,Fpatients giving such positive feedback
OL,11,Fis fantastic.J"We are really pleased
OL,12,Fwith the results of the survey.J"I
OL,13,Fwould like to thank our teams who work
OL,14,Freally hard to make sure that our
OL,15,Fpatients feel safe, supported and well
OL,16,Flooked after before, during and after
OL,17,Flabour.J"Following a Care Quality
OL,18,FCommission inspection last year, our
OL,19,Fmaternity services were rated good.
OL,20,F"While we are pleased with the
OL,21,Fresults, we are not complacent and
OL,22,Fwill be examining the results further
OL,23,Fto see where we can improve for the
OL,24,Ffuture."
